<li><a href="http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10664113-a-dance-with-dragons" rel="nofollow">A Dance with Dragons</a> <a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f1d678d37f2b0ff10bd61edee35afc16e45203c4/687474703a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f694136575363772e706e67" target="_blank"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f1d678d37f2b0ff10bd61edee35afc16e45203c4/687474703a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f694136575363772e706e67" width="30px" data-canonical-src="http://i.imgur.com/iA6WScw.png" style="max-width:100%;"></a></li>
